I’m a full time college student but I make these videos because they keep me accountable to work on what I need to do to succeed- which is feeling comfortable, studying, keeping my home a clean place & staying on top of chores, producing social media content and time managing for my final of creating a photo book :)
GRWM= get ready with me ;)

I created 3 photo books by hand about the trauma I endured after being stalked.  This was something extremely personal and hard to go through, which I worked through by creating a photo book. Swipe to see how I made the book, from the printing , to the folding , and sewing . Not to mention taking the photos , formatting and sequencing that I didn’t film. I’m incredibly proud of myself to heal from my experience in a health coping mechanism in the form of art. I encourage you to do the same with anything you’re going through: make something out of it . It’s how you survive.
Making something out of your trauma is the only way to survive .
